(2700, 1, '2018-03-12 06:26:21', '2018-03-12 06:26:21', '<p>Welcome to Royal Ambiance Beauty Salon, Put your Beauty Salon needs in our capable hands. Stretch your options when it comes to service and price. As your local Beauty Salon service provider, Royal Ambiance Salon works diligently and efficiently to get the job done for you. When locals need Beauty Salon services, they look to us as a recognized leader. We specialize in Beauty Salon, Hair Salon, Hair Extension and Styling and Weaves, and more. Before you call or look for another Beauty Salon service provider, speak to us first.&nbsp;</p><p>Our goal is to ensure you receive the best service. Our long-standing reputation means you get the most accurate industry estimates and quality service. Whatever it may be that you need, no job is too big or small for us!</p>We are a full service hair salon that cares for every hair texture,we also provide nail sevices and we do eyebrows and eyelashes.Some of our hair care products are sebastian,nioxin, alter ego, mizani, joico color system, clairol, ashtae, jane carter, the edge beauty, nu expression, design essential,nairobi ,avena and dudley .Our nail care products are from tammy taylor.<p><br></p>', 'Royal Ambiance Salon', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'royal-ambiance-salon', '', '', '2018-03-12 06:26:21', '2018-03-12 06:26:21', '', 0, 'https://listing.downtown-directory.com/beauty-salon/backup/?post_type=listing&amp;p=2700', 0, 'listing', '', 1),
